@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontName monospace
skinparam padding 5

title Workflow 3: Hybrid Scope (Macro + Micro)

actor User
participant "LLM Agent" as LLM

box "Micro Context (Local State)" #Transparent
  participant "Local Tools" as LocalTools
  participant "Live Buffer" as Buffer
end box

box "Macro Context (Project State)" #Transparent
  participant "Global Tool" as GlobalTool
  database "Project TAGS" as Tags
end box

User -> LLM : 1. Prompts issue, buffer & TAGS
LLM -> LocalTools : 2. Inspects local unsaved changes
LocalTools -> Buffer : reads live code
LLM -> GlobalTool : 3. Cross-references external calls
GlobalTool -> Tags : extracts distant definitions
LLM --> User : 4. Resolves deep structural conflicts
@enduml